---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---

<SiteLayout
  title="The thing costing your business time every day. Fixed in 30 minutes."
  description="You describe the problem. We build the fix while you watch. You leave with it running. One session. $500."
  activeNav="ai-audit"
>
  <style>
    /* Hero */
    .audit-hero { padding: 52px 0 44px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .audit-hero-inner { padding: 28px; }
    .sys-line { font-size: 0.58rem; color: var(--amber-dim); letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
    .sys-line::before { content: '>'; color: var(--amber); }
    .strip { display: flex; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0; margin-bottom: 32px; border: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .strip-item { font-size: 0.6rem; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-dim); padding: 10px 16px; border-right: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .strip-item:last-child { border-right: none; }
    .strip-item.hi { color: var(--amber); }
    .audit-hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.8rem); font-weight: 700; line-height: 0.96; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 36px; text-shadow: 0 0 28px rgba(240,192,48,0.1); }
    .audit-hero h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--amber); }
    .hero-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; gap: 36px; align-items: end; }
    .hero-desc { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--ink-dim); line-height: 1.82; max-width: 460px; }
    .hero-action { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .hero-note { font-size: 0.58rem; color: var(--ink-faint); letter-spacing: 0.04em; }

    /* Deliverables */
    .deliverable { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 52px 1fr; gap: 0 20px; padding: 28px 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .deliverable:last-child { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .del-num { font-size: 0.52rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--amber); padding-top: 3px; }
    .del-title { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 7px; }
    .del-desc { font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--ink-dim); line-height: 1.75; }

    /* Who it's for */
    .biz-grid { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0; margin-top: 20px; }
    .biz-tag { font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.04em; color: var(--ink-dim); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 9px 16px; margin: -1px 0 0 -1px; transition: background 0.15s, color 0.15s; }
    .biz-tag:hover { background: var(--amber); color: var(--bg); border-color: var(--amber); }
    .for-note { font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--amber); margin-top: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.03em; }

    /* Stats */
    .stats-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); background: var(--border); gap: 1px; margin-top: 20px; max-width: 680px; }
    .stat-cell { background: var(--bg); padding: 32px 28px; }
    .stat-num { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 700; color: var(--amber); text-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(240,192,48,0.35); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .stat-label { font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--ink-dim); line-height: 1.55; }

    /* Pricing */
    .pricing-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 360px; gap: 52px; align-items: start; }
    .pricing-note { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--ink-dim); line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 12px; }
    .pricing-card { border: 1px solid var(--amber); padding: 36px; }
    .price-label { font-size: 0.52rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--amber); margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .price-amount { font-size: 3.4rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--amber); text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(240,192,48,0.4); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .price-meta { font-size: 0.6rem; color: var(--ink-faint); letter-spacing: 0.04em; margin-bottom: 28px; }
    .price-list { list-style: none; margin-bottom: 28px; }
    .price-item { display: flex; gap: 10px; padding: 9px 0; border-top: 1px solid rgba(240,192,48,0.1); font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--ink-dim); line-height: 1.5; }
    .price-item::before { content: '+'; color: var(--amber); font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .price-footnote { font-size: 0.58rem; color: var(--ink-faint); margin-top: 10px; text-align: center; }

    /* Calendly */
    .calendly-wrap { border: 1px solid var(--border); overflow: hidden; max-width: 680px; }
    .calendly-inline-widget { min-width: 320px; height: 700px; }
    .book-contact { font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--ink-dim); margin-top: 20px; }
    .book-contact a { color: var(--amber); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; }
    .book-contact a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    /* Button variations */
    .btn--block { display: block; text-align: center; }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .hero-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .deliverable { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .del-num { margin-bottom: 4px; }
      .stats-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .pricing-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .strip { overflow-x: auto; }
    }
  </style>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <div class="audit-hero">
    <div class="box">
      <span class="box-label">// AUDIT</span>
      <div class="audit-hero-inner">
        <div class="strip">
          <span class="strip-item">30-Min Session</span>
          <span class="strip-item">Fix Built On The Call</span>
          <span class="strip-item hi">$500 Founding Rate</span>
          <span class="strip-item">First 5 Clients</span>
        </div>
        <h1>The thing costing your<br/>business time every day.<br/><em>Fixed in 30 minutes.</em></h1>
        <div class="hero-grid">
          <p class="hero-desc">
            You describe the problem. I build the fix while you watch.
            You leave with it running. No jargon, no homework, no pitch deck.
            Just the thing that was stealing your time, gone.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-action">
            <a href="#book" class="btn" aria-label="Book your session for $500">Book Your Session. $500.</a>
            <span class="hero-note">Price increases to $1,000 after 5 clients</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- What You Get -->
  <div class="section">
    <p class="sec-label">WHAT HAPPENS</p>
    <h2>Thirty minutes. You leave with something working.</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">No follow-up calls. No waiting. No surprises.</p>
    <div>
      <div class="deliverable">
        <span class="del-num">01</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="del-title">We find the biggest time drain in your business</h3>
          <p class="del-desc">You talk, I listen. We find the one thing your team does every day that shouldn't need a human. Booking confirmations, client follow-ups, missed calls, admin that piles up. Whatever's most painful.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="deliverable">
        <span class="del-num">02</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="del-title">We build the fix while you watch</h3>
          <p class="del-desc">Using tools you already have. You see it working before the call ends. Not a demo. Not a prototype. The actual thing, running.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="deliverable">
        <span class="del-num">03</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="del-title">You leave with a one-page plan</h3>
          <p class="del-desc">What was built, how many hours per week it saves you, what that's worth in dollars, and 3 other things worth fixing next. One page. No fluff.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="deliverable">
        <span class="del-num">04</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="del-title">You see exactly what's possible next</h3>
          <p class="del-desc">A clear picture of what else could stop being manual, so you know your next move if you want to keep going. No pressure. No upsell on the call.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Who It's For -->
  <div class="section">
    <p class="sec-label">WHO THIS IS FOR</p>
    <h2>You don&apos;t need to know anything about technology.</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">You just need a business where your team does the same things over and over.</p>
    <div class="biz-grid">
      <span class="biz-tag">Hair &amp; beauty salons</span>
      <span class="biz-tag">Real estate agents</span>
      <span class="biz-tag">Law offices</span>
      <span class="biz-tag">Dental &amp; medical clinics</span>
      <span class="biz-tag">Restaurants &amp; cafes</span>
      <span class="biz-tag">Contractors &amp; tradespeople</span>
      <span class="biz-tag">Fitness studios</span>
      <span class="biz-tag">Property managers</span>
    </div>
    <p class="for-note">If your team keeps doing the same thing every day, that thing should be running itself.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Stats -->
  <div class="section">
    <p class="sec-label">THE NUMBERS</p>
    <h2>What one fix actually looks like.</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Based on the Bella&apos;s Beauty Studio session. Results vary by business.</p>
    <div class="stats-grid">
      <div class="stat-cell">
        <div class="stat-num">6 hrs</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Average time saved per week from one fix</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-cell">
        <div class="stat-num">$480</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Monthly labor value recovered at $20/hr</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-cell">
        <div class="stat-num">15 min</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Customer response time vs 2 to 4 hours before</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-cell">
        <div class="stat-num">30 min</div>
        <div class="stat-label">That&apos;s all the session takes</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Pricing -->
  <div class="section">
    <p class="sec-label">PRICING</p>
    <div class="pricing-grid">
      <div>
        <h2>No retainer.<br/>No surprise fees.</h2>
        <p class="pricing-note">
          One session, one price. You see the fix working before the call ends,
          or we don&apos;t stop until it does.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <p class="price-label">Founding Rate</p>
        <div class="price-amount">$500</div>
        <p class="price-meta">flat fee &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; first 5 clients only</p>
        <ul class="price-list">
          <li class="price-item">30-minute session via Zoom</li>
          <li class="price-item">Fix built and running while you watch</li>
          <li class="price-item">One-page report: hours saved, dollar value, what&apos;s next</li>
          <li class="price-item">3 other things worth fixing in your business</li>
          <li class="price-item">Retainer proposal if you want to keep going</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#book" class="btn btn--block" aria-label="Book your session for $500">Book Now. $500.</a>
        <p class="price-footnote">Price increases to $1,000 after 5 clients.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Book -->
  <div id="book" class="section">
    <p class="sec-label">BOOK</p>
    <h2>Pick a time. We&apos;ll handle the rest.</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">30 minutes. You leave with something working.</p>
    <div class="calendly-wrap">
      <div
        class="calendly-inline-widget"
        data-url="https://calendly.com/nelson-kwesiholdings/ai-audit"
        style="min-width:320px;"
      ></div>
    </div>
    <p class="book-contact" style="margin-top:20px;">
      Questions first? DM on
      <a href="https://x.com/nelsonkwesix" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">X (@nelsonkwesix)</a>
      or
      <a href="https://instagram.com/nelsonkwesi.xyz" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Instagram (@nelsonkwesi.xyz)</a>.
    </p>
  </div>

<script is:inline src="https://assets.calendly.com/assets/external/widget.js" async></script>
</SiteLayout>
